---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Sustainability | About Heat & Glo" description="Heat & Glo's approach to manufacturing, packaging, and end-of-life material recovery. Designed for product longevity over disposability." noIndex={true}>
  <main class="max-w-page mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <p class="uppercase tracking-wide text-sm text-orange-700 font-semibold">Sustainability</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2">Built to last. Built to recover.</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-neutral-700 max-w-2xl">Heat & Glo approaches sustainability the same way the company approaches product engineering: through durability and serviceability. Fireplaces designed to last decades, with serviceable components that can be replaced in the field, contribute more to environmental outcomes than disposable alternatives marketed as "eco" but designed to be replaced.</p>
    </header>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 border-t pt-10"><a href="/about-us/" class="underline">Back to about</a></p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
